# PawPal+ Final UML Diagram
# PawPal+ Final UML Diagram

```mermaid
classDiagram

class Owner {
    +String name
    +String preferences
    +List~Pet~ pets
    +add_pet(pet)
    +get_pets()
    +get_all_tasks()
}

class Pet {
    +String name
    +String species
    +String breed
    +int age
    +List~Task~ tasks
    +add_task(task)
    +get_tasks()
}

class Task {
    +String name
    +String category
    +int duration_minutes
    +int priority
    +String time
    +String frequency
    +bool completed
    +date due_date
    +String pet_name
    +mark_complete()
    +is_high_priority()
    +create_next_occurrence()
}

class Scheduler {
    +int available_minutes
    +List~Task~ tasks
    +add_task(task)
    +sort_tasks_by_priority()
    +sort_by_time()
    +filter_by_completion(completed)
    +filter_by_pet(pet_name)
    +complete_task_and_recur(task)
    +generate_daily_plan()
    +detect_conflicts()
}

Owner "1" --> "*" Pet : owns
Pet "1" --> "*" Task : has
Scheduler "1" --> "*" Task : organizes
Task "1" --> "0..1" Task : creates next occurrence
```
